msgstr "使用给定参数初始化 CAN 总线。"

#: ../../source/unit/can.rst:127 ac59357a799c4dc1bb2d3291f6e5ebb4
msgid ""
"The value by which the CAN input clock is divided to generate the nominal"
" bit time quanta. The prescaler can be a value between 1 and 1024 "
"inclusive for classic CAN."
msgstr "CAN 输入时钟被分频以生成标称位时间量子（time quanta）的分频值。对于经典 CAN，预分频器的取值范围为 1 到 1024（含）。"

#: ../../source/unit/can.rst:128 3bceb9c2c2f442a3b141497d6afdd4da
msgid ""
"The resynchronisation jump width in units of time quanta for nominal "
"bits; it can be a value between 1 and 4 inclusive for classic CAN."
msgstr ""
"用于标称位（nominal bits）的重同步跳宽（resynchronisation jump width），单位为时间量子（time "
"quanta）；对于经典 CAN，其取值范围为 1 到 4（含）之间。"

#: ../../source/unit/can.rst:129 0265643f40a542a2961aa2a656dde9e9
msgid ""
"Defines the location of the sample point in units of the time quanta for "
"nominal bits; it can be a value between 1 and 16 inclusive for classic "
"CAN."
msgstr "定义标称位中采样点的位置，单位为时间量子；对于经典 CAN，其取值范围为 1 到 16（含）。"

#: ../../source/unit/can.rst:130 7c7983c726524193b32dd479f8a8b7ad
msgid ""
"Defines the location of the transmit point in units of the time quanta "
"for nominal bits; it can be a value between 1 and 8 inclusive for classic"
" CAN."
msgstr "以标称位的时间量子为单位定义发送点的位置；对于经典 CAN，其取值范围为 1 到 8（含）。"

#: ../../source/unit/can.rst:131 68d15d56ebac44829ca7e2fa339a0c19
msgid "is Enables triple sampling when the TWAI controller samples a bit."
msgstr "启用三重采样，当 TWAI 控制器对一个位进行采样时。"

